						<summary>

						<p><hi rend="bold">Śaka 1480 (1557 A.D.)</hi></p>						

						<p>Damaged and fragmentary. Records a gift of land by Ēkāṅgi Naraśiṅgayya, a devotee of Bhaṭṭar, for the feeding of the Śrīvaishṇavas. The details of the date viz. <hi rend="bold">Śaka 1480, Piṅgaḷa, Āśvīja ba. 10, Sunday correspond to 1557 A.D., October 17, Sunday ·37., the Saka year quoted being current.</hi> </p>						

